<font color="#D900D9">(ALL CHEERING)</font>

1007
01:27:15.982 --> 01:27:20.069
<font color="#808080">NARRATOR:</font> <i>So you see.
the story is not quite as you were told.</i>

1008
01:27:20.653 --> 01:27:22.297
